  src/signal/sigsuspend.c          SYS_rt_sigsuspend; not supported.
  src/signal/sigaltstack.c         SYS_sigaltstack; alt-stacks not
                                   supported (proving daemons don't
                                   use them).
  src/signal/sigpending.c          SYS_rt_sigpending; not supported.
  src/signal/sigtimedwait.c        SYS_rt_sigtimedwait; not supported.
  src/signal/sigqueue.c            SYS_rt_sigqueueinfo; not supported
                                   (no siginfo_t at v1.0).
  src/signal/signal.c              UNCHANGED — calls __sigaction which
                                   we've retargeted; the signal()
                                   thin-wrapper Just Works.
  src/signal/sigprocmask.c         UNCHANGED — delegates to
